    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
