    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a 2008 Chevrolet Corvette Z06, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the hand-built 7.0L LS7 V8, featuring titanium intake valves and connecting rods to minimize reciprocating mass, paired with a dry-sump lubrication system for consistent oil pressure under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. The hydroformed aluminum chassis and magnesium engine cradle provide exceptional torsional rigidity while maintaining a low curb weight. This example features the FE4 suspension package with monotube dampers and a high-performance braking system utilizing cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers. Mechanically robust with a linear power band, the vehicle displays minor cosmetic patina consistent with its well-maintained status. A visceral driving machine for the purist seeking track-capable kinematics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
